25|$|In the West, {{government}} anti-intellectualism includes nonviolent closures {{of public}} libraries and public schools, legalistic segregation of academic intellectuals to <b>the</b> <b>Ivory</b> <b>Tower,</b> and official medico-legal declarations that intellectuals tend to mental illness. Such political prostitution {{of the law}} facilitates psychiatric prosecution and imprisonment of intellectuals, usually as part of scapegoating the national intelligentsia for the dictatorship’s socioeconomic purposes, as in Fascist Italy.|$|E
